one_reviews_text:
Ive spent the my entire 2hours trying to get the graphics settings to work. Out the box the game was blurry as hell. Frames dropping left and right. I lowered the settings and eventually got to low. It looked like a bad PSVR game. Tried multiplayer and the voice chat was in and out.  I have a 1080 16gb 2400mhz /i7 4770k(4.0 ghz) According to the games specs I should be good...NOT!! The minimum specs are a farce. Oculus should be testing these specs before releasing because this sucks. What a let down.

{After UPDATE}

Just what I feared. There is going to be a long time before this game is running correctly. The update did very little for Oculus users. Explosions, kills ,etc.. cause a painful amount of stutter/lag. The game does run a tad better after update but then BOOM and your holding your breath because your snatched out of the immersion and PISSED! I tried turning my head when I mined the rocks but the whole game just pauses then the loot drops. The devs wont admit it but THIS GAME CANNOT BE RUN ON LESS THAN A 4.5 GHZ 8TH GENERATION. Oculus-" I still want a refund!"
